OddEvenByUsingSwitch
Write a C program to check the number is even or odd by using Switch Case.
Sample Input
10
Sample Output
Even


#include<stdio.h>
int main(){
    int a;
    scanf("%d",&a);

    switch(a%2==0){
        case 1:
        printf("Even");
        break;

        case 0:
        printf("Odd");
        break;
    }
}

